Description: GLEAM-X is the official R implementation of FAO’s Global Livestock Environmental
  Assessment Model (GLEAM). The package provides a modular, transparent framework for
  simulating livestock production systems and quantifying their environmental impacts.
License: AGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/un-fao/GLEAM/, https://www.fao.org/gleam/en/
